    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tongs designed with a gap for holding around an obstruction at or near one end, usually to fit over the head of a bolt in order to grip the shank of the bolt.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
